# No Changes to motorbench/ Directory

The `motorbench/` directory contains Microchip MCAF firmware generated by motorBench / MCC. **Do not create, edit, or delete any files in this directory.**

- Firmware changes are handled separately outside this project
- Read files in `motorbench/` for reference (e.g., `parameters.json`, YAML configs, header files) but never modify them
- If a firmware-side change is needed, note it as a recommendation to the user instead of making the change
